<Layout
  title="Accounting Training"
  description="Accounting and bookkeeping training in Johannesburg — journals, ledgers, bank reconciliations, financial statements and more."
  keywords="accounting training, bookkeeping training, journals, ledgers, bank reconciliation, johannesburg"
>
  <div class="section">
    <img class="image-section" alt="Accounting Training" src="/images/Training/taxtraining.jpg" />
    <h2>Accounting Training</h2>
    <p>
      Quickly get up to speed on basic bookkeeping which includes data capture into journals
      and ledgers — sales, purchase, and general journals and debtors, creditors and general
      ledgers — as well as cashbook and bank reconciliations. Debtors, creditors, invoices
      and statements will be covered.
    </p>
    <p>
      The extraction of trial balance from general ledger leading to financial statements
      and their interpretation.
    </p>
    <p>
      In addition, business plans, cashflow statements and credit control will be covered.
    </p>
    <p>
      Training will generally be part time over 3 months, though we can also put together
      a more tailored plan that suits you.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
